Package: ETM
Type: Package
Title: Embedded Topic Models - Topic Modeling with Word Embeddings
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Adji", "Dieng", email = "abd2141@columbia.edu", role = "aut"),

)
Maintainer: Porey Lin <lin.porey@gmail.com>
Description: ETM is a topic model that places words and topics in the same embedding
   space.  ETM produces interpretable topics and word embeddings that are robust to large
   vocabularies that include rare words and stop words.
